workExperiences.description:
I worked on the development of one of the main products of the largest telecommunications company in Brazil. I participated in the design and creation of the Design System and a library of reusable components for all the company's web applications. I also promoted and implemented a microfrontend architecture for the applications.

As a result, we achieved:
- More adequate separation of business contexts;
- Greater scalability potential for teams;
- Reuse of business rules with maintenance in a single codebase;
- Lower development costs;
- Better user experience.
